      <title>中国数十年来首次将经济增长目标设定在5%以下</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/business/china-gdp-target-2025.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这一目标是在共产党领导人的一次聚会上宣布的，是 1991 年以来的最低目标，可以为中国的决策计划提供线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/business/china-gdp-target-2025.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 04:21:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在风险更高的时代，中国押注于技术来抵御美国的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/world/asia/china-us-technology-trade-military.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国宣布军费开支增加7%，并制定了一项五年计划，试图减少军事和工业对西方技术的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/world/asia/china-us-technology-trade-military.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 03:59:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>戴恩斯放弃蒙大拿州连任竞选，颠覆参议院竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/elections/steve-daines-out-montana-senate-race.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员史蒂夫·戴恩斯的意外宣布可能会给民主党在这个倾向共和党的州赢得参议院多数席位的艰苦斗争带来微弱的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/elections/steve-daines-out-montana-senate-race.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 02:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普跟随他的直觉。他的国家安全顾问努力跟上。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/politics/trump-national-security.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使存在大量矛盾和不一致，决策也会很快做出。但如果没有太多的流程，就几乎没有为事情可能出错做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/politics/trump-national-security.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 02:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冈萨雷斯承认有外遇，共和党人开始谴责他</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/politics/luna-censure-gonzales.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在被迫进行决选以保住席位的第二天，众议员托尼·冈萨雷斯证实，他与一名助手有婚外情，该助手后来自杀了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/politics/luna-censure-gonzales.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 01:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>诺姆和 D.H.S.监察长就妨碍索赔提出争论</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/politics/noem-dhs-inspector-general.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国土安全部部长克里斯蒂·诺姆反驳了她所在部门的监察长，后者在一封信中告诉国会，她“系统性地阻碍”了他办公室的工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/us/politics/noem-dhs-inspector-general.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Mar 2026 23:54:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗电视和社交媒体项目对战争的挑衅和扭曲观点</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/business/media/iran-state-tv-social-media-war-ai.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管损失惨重，官方媒体和网络宣传人员仍表现出自信的姿态。部分内容是由人工智能生成的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/04/business/media/iran-state-tv-social-media-war-ai.html</guid>
